Steps to execute the code:

---------------------
On Eclipse/Netbeans:
1. Import the code directory as a project on eclipse. 
2. Add "pos/atis 0.1" or "pos/wsj 0.1" or "pos/brown 0.1" as arguments to the run configuration for all three models - BigramModel.java, BackwardBigramModel.java, BidirectionalBigramModel.java .

---------------------
On Command line:
1. $ javac code/src/nlp/lm/*.java
2. Add the pos/ directory to code/
3. To execute BigramModel, $ java -cp <root_dir>/code/src nlp.lm.BigramModel <path_to_atis_dataset> 0.1
4. To execute BackwardBigramModel, $ java -cp <root_dir>/code/src nlp.lm.BackwardBigramModel <path_to_atis_dataset> 0.1
5. To execute BidirectionalBigramModel, $ java -cp <root_dir>/code/src nlp.lm.BidirectionalBigramModel <path_to_atis_dataset> 0.1